{
  "texts": [
    "A 12-week experiment was conducted comparing videos with peer comments, videos with peer ratings and videos with peer ratings plus peer comments.",
    "The latter group provided better feedback and were most aligned with teacher scores.",
    "In the system proposed by Thamizhkanal and Kumar (2020), preprocessing and noise removal was done with the help of filtering, normalization and compression.",
    "Then internal and external segmentation was deployed.",
    "Identification of a letter in the answer script was done by convolutional neural networks."
  ]
}